00:24:37,049 --> 00:24:40,150
He just checked in.
He sort of matches the descriptions.

363
00:24:40,549 --> 00:24:42,750
Please don't disclose
my personal information.

364
00:24:42,750 --> 00:24:44,190
(A tip on Moon Seong Ho, Forward)

365
00:24:47,559 --> 00:24:51,430
