378
00:25:20,119 --> 00:25:23,059
Can we report from the scene?

379
00:25:23,059 --> 00:25:24,789
Yes. I'll set it up for you.

380
00:25:24,789 --> 00:25:25,859
Thank you.

381
00:25:28,160 --> 00:25:29,869
A while ago, an inmate named
Moon Seong Ho...

382
00:25:29,869 --> 00:25:31,400
