give us any leads.

390
00:25:48,549 --> 00:25:49,549
I see.

391
00:25:50,150 --> 00:25:51,920
How will the investigation
move forward now?

392
00:25:51,920 --> 00:25:53,460
He attacked a civilian on the run.

393
00:25:53,460 --> 00:25:55,059
We must dial it up a notch.

394
00:25:55,059 --> 00:25:57,460
We'll inspect at the checkpoints
more aggressively.

395
00:25:57,460 --> 00:25:59,660
And we'll launch
an extensive search.

396
00:26:00,430 --> 00:26:02,400
We should keep asking
for any tip-offs.

397
00:26:02,799 --> 00:26:04,869
