405
00:26:19,420 --> 00:26:22,720
You must be busy
with my father's work these days.

406
00:26:22,720 --> 00:26:25,619
When he focuses on something,
he goes all the way.

407
00:26:25,619 --> 00:26:28,390
I see. Are you talking about
the book he's about to publish?

408
00:26:28,759 --> 00:26:29,829
